Package: svgPanZoom
Title: R Htmlwidget to Add Pan and Zoom to Almost any R Graphic
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
              person(
                "Anders", "Riutta et. al.", role = c("aut", "cph"),
                comment = "svg-pan-zoom.js BSD-licensed library in htmlwidgets/lib,
                https://github.com/ariutta/svg-pan-zoom"
              ),
              person(
                "Kent", "Russell", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                comment = "R interface to svg-pan-zoom.js",
                email = "kent.russell@timelyportfolio.com"
              )
            )
Maintainer: Kent Russell <kent.russell@timelyportfolio.com>
Description: This htmlwidget provides pan and zoom
    interactivity to R graphics, including base, lattice, and ggplot2.  The
    interactivity is provided through the svg-pan-zoom.js library.  Various
    options to the widget can tailor the pan + zoom experience to nearly any
    user desire.
URL: https://github.com/timelyportfolio/svgPanZoom
BugReports: https://github.com/timelyportfolio/svgPanZoom/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
    htmlwidgets (>= 0.3.2)
Suggests:
    gridSVG,
    htmltools,
    knitr,
    SVGAnnotation,
    XML
